annotationA: Subito (Sub) is a kinesin-6 homolog. Kinesin-6 proteins are known to bundle antiparallel microtubules. Sub is required for cytokinesis in mitosis and spindle organization and chromosome segregation in female meiosis; Belongs to the TRAFAC class myosin-kinesin ATPase superfamily. Kinesin family
